            <title>[HBASE-894] [shell] Should be able to copy-paste table description to create new table</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-894</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I want to create a new table based off the description of an old.  You&apos;d think I could just copy the description of the old in the shell but it doesn&apos;t work.  Our &apos;describe&apos; emission cannot be used as input on a subsequent create.&lt;/p&gt;

